{"tid":44238,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"食微波爐野究竟係咪會致癌","createTime":"2016-12-18T06:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T09:47:57.000Z","uid":25838,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb647e12771058f6dfd1285c15f5663a7c47625","tid":44238,"uid":25838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"細個成日俾人話唔好食太多微波爐叮既野，會致癌，所以一路都好少食，但係出咗黎做野之後，好多時都冇得唔叮野食，究竟其實係咪會致癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077db760a7f1d314c26fb58308a4bf51211070d8","tid":44238,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"你咩野都唔做有有可能會<br />\n<br />\n無証據証明微波爐會致癌<br />\n你咁驚燒少次野食好過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3d6318760c7394cdce06248821013cfc9064f6","tid":44238,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/EM_Spectrum_Properties_edit.svg/2000px-EM_Spectrum_Properties_edit.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FEM_Spectrum_Properties_edit.svg%2F2000px-EM_Spectrum_Properties_edit.svg.png&h=5238c236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有野都有輻射<br />\n輻射既強弱取決於 wave length<br />\n<br />\nMicrowave 比 x-ray 弱以萬倍計<br />\n<br />\n微波爐係令帶 charge 既 particle 急速振動，產生熱量<br />\n<br />\n睇唔到微波爐點整到超高能量既 particle<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n而且，美國咁多人鍾意告大公司去屈錢<br />\n如果真係有證據證明微波爐叮野會致癌，晨早大把人告制造商 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916cdc12294c051ed8032a0488d12776ae08982d","tid":44238,"uid":7526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"食微波爐野唔係問題， 係你丁野食果時唔好企係個爐隔黎"},{"pid":"0df57c76b7050c0173366d16cf03387559e5d436","tid":44238,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"唉2016年喇⋯仲有人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f36e568cd8a6c318e82d06185b78f3ccd91619e","tid":44238,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食微波爐野唔係問題， 係你丁野食果時唔好企係個爐隔黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常嘅微波爐唔會有微波輻射泄漏<br />\n金屬外殼同爐門玻璃內側嘅金屬網會阻隔微波(原理可以Google &quot;Faraday cage&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n同埋所謂輻射致癌係講核反應製造出超高能量嘅粒子/高頻射線穿透細胞破壞DNA令細胞分裂成癌細胞, 微波爐嘅能量輸出根本唔夠能量製造呢啲粒子"},{"pid":"98970deda72adaa6dcf7bcdcdad9feed92b746d2","tid":44238,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食微波爐野唔係問題， 係你丁野食果時唔好企係個爐隔黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常嘅微波爐唔會有微波輻射泄漏<br />\n金屬外殼同爐門玻璃內側嘅金屬網會阻隔微波(原理可以Google &quot;Faraday cage&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n同埋所謂輻射致癌係講核反應製造出超高能量嘅粒子/高頻射線穿透細胞破壞DNA令細胞分裂成癌細胞, 微波爐嘅能量輸出根本唔夠能量製造呢啲粒子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你心地好好，好有耐性同愛心同關懷不同既人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d5c4be1f067eba95fe49a79c578461a19f7028","tid":44238,"uid":7526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食微波爐野唔係問題， 係你丁野食果時唔好企係個爐隔黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常嘅微波爐唔會有微波輻射泄漏<br />\n金屬外殼同爐門玻璃內側嘅金屬網會阻隔微波(原理可以Google &quot;Faraday cage&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n同埋所謂輻射致癌係講核反應製造出超高能量嘅粒子/高頻射線穿透細胞破壞DNA令細胞分裂成癌細胞, 微波爐嘅能量輸出根本唔夠能量製造呢啲粒子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    同事有實際測過<br />\n<br />\n利伸 放射師"},{"pid":"388958530d21057242a4c6cf1321fecb872f411b","tid":44238,"uid":7526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食微波爐野唔係問題， 係你丁野食果時唔好企係個爐隔黎</block